name: Existence (Prod.By Drako Beatz)
description:
"a piece of music that's just a pure expression of joy, a celebration of existence" -Jim Morrison

I go by Drako Beatz, I'm a music produce out of Dallas, Texas. 

 Ive worked with pop artist such as "TayMoneyDuh" and several artist involved in the Dallas underground scene such as "Lil Sega", "GuitarEmoji" and "Yung Coop" Ive been making about 3 beats a day for the past 5 years. I'm now introducing my work to the tezos Blockchain

This Beat is a combination of Edm Synths and hip-hop/trap Drums. The owner of this NFT has commercial rights! Enjoy!
